on init me, params
  [  0] getparam 0 .............................. <me>
  [  2] getchainedprop 33 ....................... <me.ancestor>
  [  4] getparam 1 .............................. <params>
  [  6] pusharglistnoret 2 ...................... <me.ancestor, params>
  [  8] objcall 1 ............................... me.ancestor.init(params)
  [ 10] getparam 1 .............................. <params>
