end

on getInitialGridSelection me
  [  0] getprop 2847 ............................ <pTarget>
  [  3] pushsymb 49 ............................. <#none>
  [  5] nteq .................................... <pTarget <> #none>
  [  6] jmpifz [ 24] ............................ if pTarget <> #none then
  [  9] getprop 2847 ............................ <pTarget>
  [ 12] getprop 3468 ............................ <pSym>
