  [ 24] pushsymb 49 ............................. <#none>
  [ 26] pusharglistnoret 1 ...................... <#none>
  [ 28] extcall 35 .............................. return #none
  [ 30] ret
end

on selectionMade me, theSel, theObj
  [  0] getparam 2 .............................. <theObj>
  [  2] peek 0 .................................. case theObj of
  [  4] getparam 0 .............................. <me>
  [  6] eq
  [  7] jmpifz [ 31] ............................ (case) me:
  [ 10] getparam 0 .............................. <me>
  [ 12] getparam 1 .............................. <theSel>
  [ 14] pusharglist 2 ........................... <me, theSel>
  [ 16] objcall 3469 ............................ <me.getTileSymbol(theSel)>
  [ 19] setlocal 0 .............................. commandSym = me.getTileSymbol(theSel)
